The countdown is on to the @FIAFormulaE #LondonEPrix - the first time @JaguarRacing will have competed in the #UK in over 17 years! Join @MitchEvans_ in the New #Jaguar #EPACE #PHEV as he explores the capital in full #EV mode ⚡️

@JaguarLandRoverIceAcademy
